    <stitle>HYDRO-MAX&#8482; BRAKE BOOSTER AND MASTER CYLINDER - INSTALL - RELAY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
        <title>RELAY</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk document="s04017y_14.xml" xrefid="f0401707">Figure 7</hotlnk>
            for all items in parentheses.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position relay (Item 2) in place on the relay mounting bracket (Item 4) and install torx
                head screw (Item 3). Tighten to 3 to 6 lbf-ft (4 to 8 N&#8226;m).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect wiring harness relay connector (Item 1) to the relay (Item 2).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect battery ground cable and unblock the vehicle wheels.</para>
        </step1>
        <para>Turn the ignition switch to the on position. The backup pump should run. Start engine. The backup pump
            should turn off.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
